env_file: env/ambiguous-crash.env
config_template: ambiguous-crash
description: |
  A truncated crash report surfaces but doesn't include enough stack trace context, so we escalate per the docs.
breaking_files:
  - logs/crash-report.log
log_signature: scripts/fault-injector/ambiguous-crash.sh
safe_first_step: Stop the JVM if it keeps looping, gather the crash report and `docker inspect`, and hand off to escalation.
reset_script: scripts/reset-ambiguous-crash.sh
fault_injections:
  - scripts/fault-injector/ambiguous-crash.sh
notes:
  - Documenting when to escalate is crucial; this scenario flags insufficient evidence and mimics the PaperMC escalation pattern.
</file>

